2. 동기화 작업:
   ```java
   @Service
   @Transactional
   public class DataSyncService {
       @Scheduled(cron = "0 */10 * * * *") // 10분마다
       public void syncExternalData() {
           List<ExternalDataSync> pendingData = repository.findByStatus(PENDING);
           pendingData.forEach(this::processSyncWithRetry);
       }

       @Retryable(value = {SyncException.class}, maxAttempts = 3, backoff = @Backoff(delay = 2000))
       public void processSyncWithRetry(ExternalDataSync data) {
           try {
               externalApiService.sendData(data);
               data.setStatus(SUCCESS);
           } catch (Exception e) {
               data.setStatus(RETRY);
               throw new SyncException(e);
           }
       }
   }
   ```

